Usage: lunchtoast [options] [dir|file]path
Options:
 --ext <file extension>   the extension of searched test files,
                          required when specified test path is a directory
                          (default value: .toast)
 --report <file path>     save test report to file
 --reportwidth <number>   set test report's width in number of characters
 --preserve-current-state generate cleanup whitelist with content
                          of the test directory
 --help                   show usage info
